### ===============================
### User Management
### ===============================

### Get All Users (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Users with Pagination & Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10&search=john&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Single User Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### ===============================
### User Actions
### ===============================

### Deactivate User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Activate User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Delete User (Permanent)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
